outputs.output_descr: The initiation Plan will assist in procuring services and inputs that will produce analysis of the status of the progress in respect of the MDGs and forward looking  strategies for continuing the principles post 2015 when the current initiatives ends. It will support to the preparation of a substantive analysis of the country strategies in mainstreaming the MDGs into National Development Plans and support the National consultation process on post -15 development agenda

project_title: Enhancing Nat. Cap.for Mainstre MDGs in Dev. Frameworks
